  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "3) Observation enhancement: We use corrected landmark features for enhancing observation features to combine the landmark discovery framework with different VLN agents.",
    "The enhanced observation features are adopted for final action decision.We evaluate CONSOLE on multiple mainstream VLN benchmarks, including R2R [1], REVERIE [2], R4R [3], and RxR [4].",
    "The experimental results show that CONSOLE outperforms strong baselines [16], [24] on all benchmarks.",
    "Moreover, CONSOLE achieves the new state-of-the-art on R2R and R4R in unseen scenarios.",
    "We conduct extensive insightful visualization to verify the effectiveness and necessity of different components in CONSOLE, such as the learnable scoring module and the customized designs for the prompts."
  ],
